 >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button copyButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copyButtonText<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk10\">MyObject</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">__contruct</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">$fname</span><span class=\"mtk1\">){</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk4\">$this</span><span class=\"mtk1\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk12\">filename</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$fname</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk12\">$obj</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">new</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk10\">MyObject</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk8\">&#39;file1&#39;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Class내 함수 사용</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container copyButtonContainer\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"99232340216927370000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster copyButtonToaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text copyButtonToasterText\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"customToasterText\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`print_r(\\$obj->func());`, `99232340216927370000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button copyButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copyButtonText<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk11\">print_r</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">$obj</span><span class=\"mtk1\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk11\">func</span><span class=\"mtk1\">());</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h1 id=\"5-접근-제어자\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC-%EC%A0%9C%EC%96%B4%EC%9E%90\" aria-label=\"5 접근 제어자 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. 접근 제어자</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>private, public 키워드를 사용해서 접근을 제어할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"6-상속\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-%EC%83%81%EC%86%8D\" aria-label=\"6 상속 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. 상속</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>extends 키워드를 사용해 클래스를 상속할 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Tip!!</strong><br>\n클래스 안에 static 키워드를 추가한 변수를 만들어주면 모든 인스턴스가 공유하는 변수를 만들어줄 수 있다.</p>\n<div\n              class=\"gatsby-code-button-container copyButtonContainer\"\n              data-toaster-id=\"17879075829295866000\"\n              data-toaster-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster copyButtonToaster\"\n              data-toaster-text-class=\"gatsby-code-button-toaster-text copyButtonToasterText\"\n              data-toaster-text=\"customToasterText\"\n              data-toaster-duration=\"3500\"\n              onClick=\"copyToClipboard(`class car{\n  private static \\$count = 0;\n  private \\$name;\n  function __construct(\\$name){\n    \\$this->name = \\$name;\n    self::\\$count = self::\\$count+1;\n  }\n}`, `17879075829295866000`)\"\n            >\n              <div\n                class=\"gatsby-code-button copyButtonClass\"\n                data-tooltip=\"\"\n              >\n                copyButtonText<svg class=\"gatsby-code-button-icon\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"none\" d=\"M0 0h24v24H0V0z\"/><path d=\"M16 1H2v16h2V3h12V1zm-1 4l6 6v12H6V5h9zm-1 7h5.5L14 6.5V12z\"/></svg>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container default-dark\" data-language=\"php\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk4\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk10\">car</span><span class=\"mtk1\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">private</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">static</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$count</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk7\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">private</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk4\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk11\">__construct</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk12\">$name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">){</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk4\">$this</span><span class=\"mtk1\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"mtk12\">name</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk12\">$name</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk4\">self</span><span class=\"mtk1\">::</span><span class=\"mtk12\">$count</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> = </span><span class=\"mtk4\">self</span><span class=\"mtk1\">::</span><span class=\"mtk12\">$count</span><span class=\"mtk1\">+</span><span class=\"mtk7\">1</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"클래스-접근\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%81%B4%EB%9E%98%EC%8A%A4-%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC\" aria-label=\"클래스 접근 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>클래스 접근</h3>\n<p>부모 클래스를 접근할 때는 parent(parent::) 연산자를 사용한다.\n자신의 클래스를 접근할 때는 self(self::) 연산자를 사용한다.</p>\n<p><strong>::는 new 지시자로 class를 미리 객체화 시켜놓지 않고 사용하는 시점에서 객체가 생성되고 지정된 메소드가 실행되도록 하는 접근자이다.</strong></p>\n<h1 id=\"7-namespace-use\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-namespace-use\" aria-label=\"7 namespace use permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>7. Namespace, use</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Namespace : 동일한 이름을 가진 class가 존재할 때 구분하여 사용하기 위한 이름\nuse : 키워드를 통해 불러올 수 있다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Java에서 package와 import 같은 개념이다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-4/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"